| Operation              | Isolation Level                    | Reasoning                                    |
|------------------------|------------------------------------|----------------------------------------------|
| Course Enrollment      | SERIALIZABLE                       | Last seat race condition                     |
| Drop Course            | SERIALIZABLE                       | Atomic drop + waitlist promotion             |
| Batch Enrollment       | READ COMMITTED                     | Independent operations, better concurrency   |
| Waitlist Management    | SERIALIZABLE                       | Position integrity critical                  |
| Reports/Statistics     | REPEATABLE READ + READ ONLY        | Consistent snapshot, no blocking             |
